contents: It is the color of the sky
grey with no shades of purple
bright purple with no greyish tones
purplish mauve paler than the other two colors
pinkish not as grey as the other pink
grey neutral with no brown tint
bright green does not look like pea soup
the one with the most pink
the one that is the most greyish
blue purple not grey and not bright
the purple with the most red in it, but not the pink one
greenish not too yellow not too brown
